        <p class="text-xl text-[#c0caf5] mb-8" data-en="Interested in working together? Let's talk!" data-es="¿Interesado en trabajar juntos? ¡Hablemos!">
          Interested in working together? Let's talk!
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
